  "text": "The conformational structure of the EPS in solution was determined by the addition of Congo Red, which forms complexes with EPS. The transition from a triple helix arrangement to the single-stranded conformation was determined by measuring the absorbance at λ max = 400-800 nm of Congo Red and EPS solution aft er the addition of 0 to 0.5 mol/L of NaOH with the UV-Vis spectrophotometer (TU-1800; Beĳ ing Purkinje General Instrument Co. Ltd., Beĳ ing, PR China) according to our previous report [CITATION_1] .",
